OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSunny spells
OL,6,Fand a few scattered showers in the
OL,7,Fevening, the showers mainly over
OL,8,FArgyll. Overnight showers isolated
OL,9,Fwith most places dry with some longer
OL,10,Fclear spells developing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA bright and mostly sunny
OL,13,Fstart. Cloud increasing through the
OL,14,Fmorning with perhaps the odd light
OL,15,Fshower, before sunny spells develop
OL,16,Fagain later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
